Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Signs
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bokura no Senjou
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Giraffe Blues
Comment: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichido dake no Koi nara
Comment: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Zettai Reido Super Novatic
Comment: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,ED Super Novatic
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.10,0:00:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Interceptamos uma transmissão da NUNS.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A 47ª Frota Especial parece ter sido aniquilada.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.94,0:00:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aniquilada?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.74,0:00:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aparentemente, seus Devoradores de Dimensão fizeram uma detonação em si mesmos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.69,0:00:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Foram detectadas também poderosas ondas de bio-dobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,O canto das estrelas, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades fiquem prontas para dobrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.53,0:00:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Destino: Ragna!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,É hora da batalha final.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Caramba, estou ficando nervoso(a).
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.88,0:00:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.10,0:00:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos sair dessa bagunça vivos.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.99,0:00:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho que ir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Então este é o Santuário Estelar?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu conheço este lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Este é o meu palco.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.36,0:01:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu podia sentir o vento de dezenas de milhares de vidas sendo extintas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,É este o fardo que Pai teve que carregar?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.39,0:01:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,É o destino daqueles que governam as estrelas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Keith...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Então todos têm carregado este peso?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,De agora em diante, eu também participarei disso.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.65,0:01:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, Vossa Majestade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas não é minha intenção derramar sangue desnecessariamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Agora que testemunharam o poder do canto das estrelas,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou iniciar negociações de paz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Vossa Majestade?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu encerrarei esta luta de uma vez por todas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vou iniciar os preparativos para o lançamento.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Por favor, perdoe-me por sentar no seu trono,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,mas comandar o Cantor Estelar drena a runa do controlador.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenha cautela.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, Vossa Majestade.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,O vento está enchendo meu corpo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu consigo sentir a dor latejante dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.41,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,É tão solitário.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pela galáxia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelos nossos entes queridos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelo bem de Makina e Mikumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.76,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...queimar em branco-quente...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.88,0:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...e nos divertir como se nossas vidas dependessem disso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Frota inimiga detectada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Múltiplas embarcações se aproximando!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Líder Delta, para o pelotão:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.68,0:02:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Iniciar Operação Ragnarök!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.41,0:02:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dessem o máximo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou levar Ragna de volta!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Delta 4, como está seu novo caça?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.45,0:02:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Incrível.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Está funcionando muito bem com os dados de voo do Messer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Vou mostrar a eles que posso voar sem pensar demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos fazer isso, Mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estou com vocês, garotas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Vão!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja... O que aconteceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja Wion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,O vento dela está diferente agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Como se o sol dela tivesse sido bloqueado por nuvens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Cavaleiro Branco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate Immelmann.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Estamos prontos para o lançamento.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suas ordens?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.86,0:04:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Como rei verdadeiro, eu ordeno:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudanjaar Rom Mayan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta música...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser! Ondas bio-dobráveis amplificando exponencialmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Essa é a Cantora Estelar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Belo! A rede neural de dobra está tomando forma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Qual é o significado disso, Roid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ao sincronizar as mentes de todos os humanoides,\Nevoluiremos para algo maior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Evoluir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.91,0:06:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Este é o verdadeiro poder do canto das estrelas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todos os humanoides serão conectados e evoluirão para um único ser superior.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isso deve trazer paz absoluta à galáxia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Você quer trair Sua Majestade e Windermere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Não há traição nisso.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Os humanoides evoluirão para uma forma de vida em escala galáctica, semelhante ao Vajra.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No cerne disso estaremos nós,\Nos Windermerianos, que possuímos runas.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ao conectar bilhões de mentes, nossa velocidade de processamento de informação atingirá níveis divinos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sentiremos cada momento como uma eternidade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poderemos ser libertados das correntes de nossas vidas passageiras e governar a galáxia para sempre.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Roid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Seu bastardo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Um novo mundo nasce!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,O que foi que eu—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Agora você e eu somos um com a galáxia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Deixem nossas vozes ressoar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Este é o propósito da minha vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu devo...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Devo fazer minha canção alcançá-los!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.88,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,O vento da vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vossa Majestade?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Desativar o Roid?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Trabalhar com a Walküre?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vocês querem que nós os perdoemos?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eu não peço isso de vocês.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O Governo da ONU deve ser lidado eventualmente.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:09:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mas esta é nossa prioridade agora!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.37,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isso pertence a Vossa Majestade...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pelo vento verdadeiro,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,derrotem o Roid Brehm e protejam a galáxia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelo Grande Vento!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga... Da!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tentar se manter é fútil.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Torne-se um comigo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unidos.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Me solte!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.25,0:10:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu quero... proteger... Freyja...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu te amo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.50,0:10:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Te protegerei não importa o que aconteça!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Então faça sua canção ressoar pela galáxia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sua mão...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Por favor, não conte a ninguém.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Quero passar o pouco tempo que me resta no palco.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(2073,2532,\1c&H000000&)}Eu sou parte de Walküre!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu te amo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu nasci em uma família de pilotos.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Passei minha vida sentindo que eu tinha que voar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas aí eu te conheci,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,e ao voarmos juntos, cheguei a perceber
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,o quanto eu amo voar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu queria poder voar com você para sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirage...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Até quando você vai ficar em silêncio, Freyja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Você me fez dizer tudo isso, mas você não vai dizer nada por si mesma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Covarde! Sem espinha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.08,0:12:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Garota mimada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Mirage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu te amo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1821,2238,1,\1c&HF4F4F4&\3c&HF4F4F4&\4c&HF4F4F4&)}Eu te amo... Eu te amo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu te amo... Eu te amo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu te amo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu te amo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Amo você quando você voa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Amo você quando você ama voar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu também te amo, Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As regras do poder rúnico!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.20,0:13:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname! Reina!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Uma música?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Walküre?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.05,0:13:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Esta canção?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,É a garota da maçã!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que a minha runa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Pew! Pew! Pew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.65,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Esta música...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O que eu sou...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Não seja enganado, Rudanjaar Rom Mayan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudanjaar Rom Mayan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudanjaar Rom Mayan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isto é o Lord Roid?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Rudanjaar Rom Mayan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Avancem! Resgatem o Mikumo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sim, senhor!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:31.26,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recebido!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Não há necessidade de ordens!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Fiquem atentos às costas!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.95,0:14:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Não abaixe a guarda por causa da empolgação, garoto safado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, cala a boca, intrusa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado(a), Mirage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Me agradece depois.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Makina!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:55.45,Alt,,0,0,0,,Viva!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu queria tanto cantar com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que você não vem comigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Garotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu pude cantar com a Walküre,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Encontrei o amor da minha vida,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,e minha runa está tão cheia de vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo, que tipo de sentimento você coloca nas suas canções?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Não... Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Música é amor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Música é esperança!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Música é vida!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.15,0:15:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Música é energia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Desde que eu conheci todas vocês...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu só quero...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.15,0:16:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,cantar juntas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Música é mistério!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.81,0:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela revivou.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumo-Kumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Walküre!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Suporte?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A canção deles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Walküre!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele nos salvou?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas desta vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Avante!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparem-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ataque Éter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Keith...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Freyja!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Segure firme!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Chegamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Keit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pegue o Cantor das Estrelas!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O quê?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou parar o vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cavaleiro Branco...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que você não entende?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Você deve ter sentido os céus também!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A eternidade além de nossas vidas passageiras!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Poderíamos viver para sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,O presente é tudo para mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Naquele momento, senti a luz ardente da vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Foi você quem me mostrou isso, Roid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu fiz?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cavaleiro Branco!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as forças: avaliem nossos danos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.27,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Voltaremos para Windermere no momento em que estivermos prontos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sim.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sim!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No final, Keith e Roid voaram os céus de Windermere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos de volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.66,0:20:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim. Os céus de Ragnan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Marianne!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kumo-Kumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo de volta, Kumo-Kumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.07,0:21:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindos de volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Makina... Reina...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaname!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo de volta, Mikumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Que bom estar de volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,O céu está alto
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,e sua runa brilha intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,O mar é azul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,As nuvens são grandes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Os mercados são macios e fofos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A praia é branca.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.56,0:22:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,O vento é gentil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.48,0:22:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.20,0:22:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Estaremos sempre juntos.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.96,0:22:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,É melhor estar pronto.
